{"tid":772983,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中共軍新驅逐艦 或會命名「台北號」","createTime":"2018-08-09T07:29:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T07:55:36.000Z","uid":184679,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0318d389cc444b427bb3f6247b271baf344a6915","tid":772983,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:29:22.000Z","msg":"《環球時報》軍事微信公眾號指出，解放軍全力建造號稱戰鬥力最強的055型驅逐艦，過去13個月已有4艘下水，另有4艘在建造中，報道稱這些艦艇將會以「省會城市」命名，很可能會出現「台北號」戰艦。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，根據中國《海軍艦艇命名條例》，驅逐艦、護衞艦是以中國大、中型城市命名，近年解放軍海軍軍艦發展蓬勃，大批新型驅逐艦陸續下水，目前中國已有25個省會城市名被用於軍艦命名，目前還沒有被公開正式用於軍艦命名的「省會型」城市，只剩下西藏拉薩、廣西南寧、江西南昌，與及「台灣台北」。<br />\n<br />\n有評論認為，「倘若『台北號』名稱雀屏中選，未來可能出現台北艦繞台，甚至上演兩岸台北艦在台海遭遇的畫面」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣網民諷刺地稱：「那再來三艘，一艘叫日本號，一艘叫韓國號，一艘叫菲律賓號，都給你管就好啦！還等甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180808/58538335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F58538335&d=aQF%2BqNc8xvVqZsVdJcXYY54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d36bcb58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F58538335&h=dd96b5c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180808/58538335</a>"},{"pid":"4bf055fa605fc2a10f125eed470d3a12803bbc0f","tid":772983,"uid":9230,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0318d389cc444b427bb3f6247b271baf344a6915","tid":772983,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:29:22.000Z","msg":"《環球時報》軍事微信公眾號指出，解放軍全力建造號稱戰鬥力最強的055型驅逐艦，過去13個月已有4艘下水，另有4艘在建造中，報道稱這些艦艇將會以「省會城市」命名，很可能會出現「台北號」戰艦。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，根據中國《海軍艦艇命名條例》，驅逐艦、護衞艦是以中國大、中型城市命名，近年解放軍海軍軍艦發展蓬勃，大批新型驅逐艦陸續下水，目前中國已有25個省會城市名被用於軍艦命名，目前還沒有被公開正式用於軍艦命名的「省會型」城市，只剩下西藏拉薩、廣西南寧、江西南昌，與及「台灣台北」。<br />\n<br />\n有評論認為，「倘若『台北號』名稱雀屏中選，未來可能出現台北艦繞台，甚至上演兩岸台北艦在台海遭遇的畫面」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣網民諷刺地稱：「那再來三艘，一艘叫日本號，一艘叫韓國號，一艘叫菲律賓號，都給你管就好啦！還等甚麼？」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180808/58538335\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F58538335&d=aQF%2BqNc8xvVqZsVdJcXYY54f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=d36bcb58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180808%2F58538335&h=dd96b5c5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180808/58538335</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:32:18.000Z","msg":"台北號被擊沉，會唔會有傻豬以為台軍打輸咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8586ab7718b4602e075c4d9220588f6bd0eefd32","tid":772983,"uid":1247,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"霸道到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己改隻美國號咁就連美國都係中國既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲唔成為最後贏家？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0e1cad5e8a756e9fc67621bac71a4c50036b00c","tid":772983,"uid":136186,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:37:56.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c50ef0fbb1fa00e06eea9fd42632086449f9279","tid":772983,"uid":146621,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8586ab7718b4602e075c4d9220588f6bd0eefd32","tid":772983,"uid":1247,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T07:33:19.000Z","msg":"霸道到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n自己改隻美國號咁就連美國都係中國既<img src